                    <div>Get <strong>detailed reports</strong> on your progress</div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="expanded-view">
            <h1>My Monthly Savings Program</h1>
            <div class="expanded-info">
                <img src="/public/images/image.jpg" class="main-image">
                <p>
                    Learn how you can <strong>set aside money for your future goals</strong>, whether you're saving for education,
                    a new addition to your home, or that special vacation you've been wanting to go on!
                </p>
                <p>
                    Our "My Monthly Savings" program allows you to specify <strong>how much you want to save</strong> each month.
                    The amount is completely flexible; you can set this once, or you change this amount as often as needed.
                </p>
                <p>
                    Our <strong>Savings Calculator</strong> can help you figure out <strong>how much to save each month</strong>
                    in order to reach a specific savings goal, taking the mystery out of monthly savings.
                </p>
                <p>
                    And you get <strong>monthly reports</strong> showing your savings activity, with helpful guidance on how to
                    get the most out of your savings.
                </p>
                <button class="cta-btn">Sign up today!</button>
            </div>
        </div>

